# Neahttadigis√°nit fab cheat sheet:

Command                    What it does
-------------------------------------------------------------
fab update PROJECT         Updates dictionaries sources
                           (pulls from github)
fab compile PROJECT        Compiles dictionary from sources
                           (do this after update)
fab restart PROJECT        Restarts the server for PROJECT
                           (do this after compiling dictionaries)
fab strings extract        Compile translation strings
                           (do this after adding translations)
fab strings compile        Compile .po to .mo (all dictionaries)
                           (do this after adding translations)
fab test PROJECT           Checks configuration and FST files
fab add-stem               Adds stem information to smenob
fab ls                     List projects (baakoeh, sanit, sanat, etc)
                           (use fab ls --help for more info)
fab --help                 Shows commands, general info
fab compile --help         Shows help on "compile" command

The commands are defined in neahtta/fab_commands.py.
